Comment: 0,0:00:00.95,0:00:00.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,==========Avant==========
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.31,0:00:09.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.07,0:00:12.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是我的究极香水
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.45,0:00:15.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Men
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.31,0:00:41.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这件事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.14,0:00:47.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开始于玛古诺利亚的一个角落
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.65,0:00:50.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点走吧 蕾比还等着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.20,0:00:55.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙在干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.16,0:00:56.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.24,0:00:58.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.62,0:01:00.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身体不舒服吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.41,0:01:05.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Men
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.37,0:01:08.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓝色天马的一夜？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.33,0:01:10.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你来玛古诺利亚干什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.01,0:01:15.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂 这么了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.09,0:01:17.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说一夜是这个体格么？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.72,0:01:19.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.18,0:01:23.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快…快停下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.44,0:01:30.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Men
Comment: 0,0:00:00.95,0:00:00.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,==========Main==========
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.38,0:03:18.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 这份零工是怎么回事嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.26,0:03:22.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要抱怨好好工作
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.22,0:03:26.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天可是8island玛古诺利亚店的开业纪念日啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.77,0:03:29.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开了2号店
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.10,0:03:33.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们几个还想偷懒到什么时候
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.56,0:03:34.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.19,0:03:37.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为是休息时间 不经意就…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.94,0:03:39.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来 艾露莎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.44,0:03:40.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请看看这个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.86,0:03:42.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,周刊志怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.82,0:03:43.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.62,0:03:47.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帅哥魔法师排行榜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.24,0:03:49.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 每周还有这类报道的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.87,0:03:54.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快看这里 灰大人也榜上有名呢 好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.71,0:03:58.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？说起帅哥的话 不是应该指的一夜那样的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.09,0:04:00.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.55,0:04:00.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Men
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.97,0:04:04.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看啊 那家伙不是一直都自夸俊美无双吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.09,0:04:07.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是啦 那是他王婆卖瓜 自卖自夸啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.31,0:04:13.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看 灰大人和其他魔法师们和一夜完全不一样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.27,0:04:17.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊 我弄错了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.77,0:04:20.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾露莎总是让人充满了「惊喜」啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.90,0:04:22.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.28,0:04:24.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说杰德和特洛伊好慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.49,0:04:29.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明还激动地说小蕾比的婚纱装绝对要看什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.71,0:04:35.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 说曹操曹操到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.58,0:04:37.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蕾比…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.96,0:04:38.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蕾比…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.17,0:04:42.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 来太晚了…吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.97,0:04:53.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Men
Comment: 0,0:04:54.23,0:05:00.65,Title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord6\fad(524,0)\pos(640,681)}FAIRY TAIL of the DEAD MEEEEEEEEEN
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.28,0:05:07.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一夜？这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.07,0:05:10.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得我的精神受到了严重创伤
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.37,0:05:13.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,温蒂你要坚强一些
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.50,0:05:15.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下 你们要干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.66,0:05:18.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要啊 不要闻过来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.96,0:05:19.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小蕾比
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.84,0:05:21.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能过去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.42,0:05:23.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得绝对不能靠近啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.46,0:05:25.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是… 小蕾比她
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.01,0:05:30.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在叫我吗 小露
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.55,0:05:32.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Men
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.97,0:05:36.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.81,0:05:38.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被闻到就会传染吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.15,0:05:40.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们还是快从这里逃走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.82,0:05:43.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶的一夜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.69,0:05:45.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和我一决胜负吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.86,0:05:49.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Men Men
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.78,0:05:50.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.45,0:05:52.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.04,0:05:54.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾露莎 你要小心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.75,0:05:57.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是被闻到 就会变成一夜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.75,0:05:58.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.83,0:06:02.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用担心 这些一夜的行动好像很迟钝的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.84,0:06:09.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,矢岛先生也快点逃比较…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.56,0:06:15.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.45,0:06:31.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要 不要 快住手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.49,0:06:34.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Men
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.33,0:06:42.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办 城里被一夜…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.96,0:06:44.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底要怎么办才好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.96,0:06:47.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？露西不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.26,0:06:49.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是跑散了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.26,0:06:51.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟她的行头不太适合跑动呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.26,0:06:56.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你们没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.77,0:06:57.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是灰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.89,0:07:01.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真正的帅哥来救茱比亚了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.15,0:07:08.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这到底是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.44,0:07:10.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全城都是一夜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.49,0:07:11.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公会里怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.16,0:07:16.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简直不忍直视
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.96,0:07:24.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Men
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.71,0:07:26.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在连公会都回不去了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.71,0:07:32.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特别是变成一夜的拉克萨斯 完全无法接近
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.76,0:07:34.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使变成一夜也还是一样强啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.97,0:07:36.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Men
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.18,0:07:39.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有其他没中招的家伙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.85,0:07:41.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许还有艾露莎和露西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.35,0:07:43.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是已经走散了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.44,0:07:47.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灰大人 我好害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.32,0:07:48.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茱比亚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.78,0:07:52.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.28,0:07:56.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我闻一下就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.37,0:07:59.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是好味道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.08,0:08:01.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Men
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.84,0:08:15.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都没事吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.97,0:08:21.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是久违的远足呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.10,0:08:22.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.48,0:08:25.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔扎克 碧斯卡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.19,0:08:26.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小阿丝卡好像也没事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.86,0:08:29.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.78,0:08:32.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,碧斯卡 我爱你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.32,0:08:34.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是 阿尔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.16,0:08:39.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Men
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.37,0:08:43.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Men
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.38,0:08:49.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里已经是地狱了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.88,0:08:53.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办 怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.92,0:08:58.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们…都会变成一夜的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.16,0:09:27.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.46,0:09:34.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.05,0:09:39.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全玛古诺利亚的人一定都会变成一夜的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.26,0:09:42.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以这种扩散感染的速度…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.06,0:09:46.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,费奥雷全境都会被传染
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.31,0:09:49.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根本没有可逃之处的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.40,0:09:52.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其他公会的大家也…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.74,0:09:57.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,评议院也会…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.03,0:10:00.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就连王都也不例外
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.83,0:10:08.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里…就是玛古诺利亚终结的开始
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.88,0:10:15.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是露西的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.67,0:10:17.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起来好像没事的说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.93,0:10:24.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏 哈比
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.36,0:10:35.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊 连蕾比他们也…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.82,0:10:43.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏露露和温蒂她们没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.41,0:10:47.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.12,0:10:50.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会吧 矢岛先生也…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.58,0:10:51.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾露莎怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.08,0:10:55.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在被变成一夜的蕾比她们袭击的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.05,0:10:56.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,矢岛先生是和艾露莎在一起的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.01,0:10:58.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没准已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.01,0:11:00.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Men
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.18,0:11:05.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光是想象一下 那破坏力就简直要醉了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.44,0:11:14.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里应该安全吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.56,0:11:15.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我肚子饿了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.02,0:11:18.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少躲在食物仓库里的话还好一点…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.07,0:11:21.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说 到底发生什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.53,0:11:23.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然不知道发生了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.28,0:11:27.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被一夜化的人闻到的话 好像就会被感染呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.74,0:11:29.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简直就像一夜病毒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.00,0:11:34.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然循着气味来找大家 但都已经晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.71,0:11:37.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一夜们也是冲着气味在找人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.75,0:11:41.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你因为穿着那个衣服 不怎么分辨得出气味了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.59,0:11:43.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得感谢这件奇怪的衣服啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.39,0:11:47.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说 你们为啥没事？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.22,0:11:47.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.06,0:11:49.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.56,0:11:51.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 你在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.98,0:11:55.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快看快看 我发现了鱼图案的毛巾
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.40,0:12:02.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Men
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.87,0:12:07.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.99,0:12:09.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 这里已经被发现了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.00,0:12:11.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起的说
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.06,0:00:00.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.55,0:12:23.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之这个城市已经完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.80,0:12:26.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能走下水道逃出这个城市了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.76,0:12:30.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 是不是只能找无人岛去避难了呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.60,0:12:33.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 我好像闻到了什么味道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.64,0:12:34.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里到处都是污水还能闻到？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.81,0:12:35.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快别说了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.23,0:12:38.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.65,0:12:39.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,躲开点
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.74,0:12:44.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到你了哦 火龙神 Men
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.82,0:12:47.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可别小看了灭龙魔法师的鼻子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.03,0:12:49.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一夜化的…伽吉鲁？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.12,0:12:51.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是伽吉鲁的一夜？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.04,0:12:53.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种事都无所谓吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.75,0:12:54.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Men
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.29,0:12:56.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连力利都…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.08,0:12:59.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快逃 被近身闻到的话就完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.67,0:13:04.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我等等
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.88,0:13:07.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逃也是没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.09,0:13:10.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看样子他们的行动很迟缓的说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.97,0:13:12.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好嘞 走这边
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.02,0:13:14.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行动好不方便
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.56,0:13:18.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Men 火龙神 哈比
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.27,0:13:19.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Men
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.65,0:13:22.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们…没有觉察到露西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.74,0:13:25.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个衣服好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.28,0:13:28.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好 我想到了个好点子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.46,0:13:43.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火龙神 Men
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.30,0:13:46.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈比 Men
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.72,0:13:47.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.63,0:13:49.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛苦的说 夏
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.30,0:13:50.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别说话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.35,0:13:51.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一身汗臭啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.18,0:13:53.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别说话 气息都喷到我后背上了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.52,0:13:55.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.86,0:14:04.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.49,0:14:07.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗梅…不对 罗密欧？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.90,0:14:08.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,温蒂姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.16,0:14:09.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.28,0:14:14.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 但是爸爸已经不行了 瓦卡巴叔叔也是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.45,0:14:16.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Men
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.04,0:14:19.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底会变成什么样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.79,0:14:21.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能说丧气话哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.84,0:14:25.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好像找到他们的弱点了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.46,0:14:27.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.42,0:14:29.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有件事想确认一下 跟我来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.64,0:14:36.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会让你们逃跑的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.98,0:14:38.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Men
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.06,0:14:40.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.27,0:14:41.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边也…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.48,0:14:43.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.99,0:14:53.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被闻味道也是时间问题了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.78,0:14:55.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又不能和他们战斗…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.41,0:14:58.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,温蒂姐 和夏露露一起飞走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.12,0:15:00.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是那样的话罗密欧你就…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.96,0:15:03.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要管我 比起这个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.17,0:15:05.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到了空中就去找夏哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.21,0:15:08.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏？为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.30,0:15:09.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,温蒂 我们得走了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.38,0:15:12.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉了 罗密欧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.51,0:15:13.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗密欧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.72,0:15:15.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托你了 温蒂姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.10,0:15:18.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏哥哥的话 一定可以…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.60,0:15:19.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗密欧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.23,0:15:21.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要看 温蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.57,0:15:30.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在不是哭的时候 温蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.32,0:15:35.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能让罗密欧的牺牲白费 我们赶快去找夏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.99,0:15:36.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.79,0:15:41.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 什么好点子嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.75,0:15:43.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难得的防护服的说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.08,0:15:46.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想法本身我觉得还是很好的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.59,0:15:47.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.38,0:15:50.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 应该差不多能走出玛古诺利亚了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.26,0:15:54.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么声音
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.39,0:15:56.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 在下水道鼻子都不灵了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.51,0:15:58.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.43,0:15:59.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.18,0:16:01.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在那里啊 火龙神
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.60,0:16:06.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有露西也是 真是不错的气味
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.77,0:16:08.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏 那边也有人过来了的说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.48,0:16:09.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.78,0:16:11.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,后面也…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.78,0:16:13.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被包围了的说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.45,0:16:14.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没地方逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.62,0:16:17.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来只好杀出一条血路逃跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.74,0:16:18.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太乱来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.95,0:16:19.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈比
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.62,0:16:21.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.29,0:16:22.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露西 到背上来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.83,0:16:23.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.37,0:16:28.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然你们这么想闻味道的话 就让你们闻个够吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.21,0:16:29.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火龙的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.38,0:16:32.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咆哮
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.45,0:17:04.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好…好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.33,0:17:07.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玛古诺利亚到处都是一夜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.63,0:17:08.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这太可怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.46,0:17:12.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏 带着两个人飞太勉强了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.92,0:17:14.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油啊哈比
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.22,0:17:17.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好…好重
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.39,0:17:18.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.51,0:17:20.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈比 露西也在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.31,0:17:21.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.31,0:17:22.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们两个都没事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.39,0:17:26.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏露露 你没事真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.14,0:17:27.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说哈比…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.31,0:17:31.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏 罗密欧好像发现了一夜他们的弱点
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.23,0:17:32.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.15,0:17:35.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然罗密欧已经沦陷了…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.28,0:17:36.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.61,0:17:39.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗密欧让我们来找夏
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.99,0:17:41.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.33,0:17:43.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(230,710)}夏…要掉下去了的说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.00,0:17:44.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗密欧说找我？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.95,0:17:46.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(230,710)}要掉了掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.29,0:17:51.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏 手要断了的说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.80,0:17:53.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.55,0:17:54.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.42,0:17:55.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道什么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.92,0:17:57.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露西 放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.64,0:17:59.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行了 快听话照做
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.14,0:18:01.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的可以信你吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.72,0:18:02.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.10,0:18:05.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏 那就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.68,0:18:07.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.41,0:18:26.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还好一夜他们行动很迟缓呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.25,0:18:27.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不愧是夏
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.75,0:18:30.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好沉…手要断了的说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.21,0:18:31.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在还要说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.88,0:18:34.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 这是朝着哪里去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.67,0:18:38.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇怪 但是那个方向是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.88,0:18:40.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你们几个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.84,0:18:41.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.89,0:18:44.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有味儿 又没有洗澡吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.93,0:18:47.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为真的很麻烦嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.48,0:18:48.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.48,0:18:52.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一两天不洗澡也没什么关系吧 艾露莎姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.65,0:18:56.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天可是矢岛先生的开店纪念日啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.19,0:18:59.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们不会是想就这么去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.88,0:19:15.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,借你们这个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.84,0:19:16.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.30,0:19:18.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除臭剂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.26,0:19:21.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后可要好好去洗个澡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.43,0:19:22.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除臭剂？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.77,0:19:31.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.85,0:19:33.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用了这个就没味道了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.77,0:19:35.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏哥哥 也借我用用
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.65,0:19:36.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咱也要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.23,0:19:42.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙鼻子那么灵 却对自己的味道毫不在意吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.26,0:20:04.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.26,0:20:06.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉克萨斯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.81,0:20:11.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Men 真是不错的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.98,0:20:14.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在可没空和你玩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.15,0:20:17.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.07,0:20:21.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Men
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.99,0:20:24.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尝尝这个
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.33,0:20:35.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.30,0:20:44.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 夏…这都是什么情况啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.47,0:20:47.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好嘞 大家都快变回原样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.40,0:21:01.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 开什么玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.99,0:21:04.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当时真以为要不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.24,0:21:06.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是可怕呢 一夜病毒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.03,0:21:09.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果那到底是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.53,0:21:12.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是一夜开发的帅哥药
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.75,0:21:14.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Men
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.42,0:21:19.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到会入侵到玛古诺日亚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.25,0:21:21.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是对帅哥的…执念吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.67,0:21:26.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经一下子就被认定为魔法禁药了 可以放心了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.01,0:21:29.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Men
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.10,0:21:30.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这也是当然的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.76,0:21:34.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一想到如果没有除臭剂的情况 就让人毛骨悚然呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.68,0:21:41.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也有知道自己变成了一夜 一时半会儿振作不起来的人在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.73,0:21:43.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来艾露莎也变了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.28,0:21:45.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真敢说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.99,0:21:46.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一团乱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.11,0:21:48.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经嫁不出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.07,0:21:50.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们太大惊小怪了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.91,0:21:53.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来真是大功一件呢 夏
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.54,0:21:54.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.66,0:21:56.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是帅哥也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.46,0:21:59.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要心地好就可以了
